                Min, Hour, week, month 
    information coming from server
        - A1 = customer info if is a private customer or company customer 
        - A2 = frist address with vaild ( street + Number + city)
        - A3 = number of Tour ( gust-id , plz hex , trip_id)
        - A4 = start day (with system help same day)
        - A5 - finish day (empty when the tour have no finish day)
        - A6 - start hour (with help from system start 8:00 till 9:00 Uhr)
        - A7 - finish hour (with help from system finish 9:00 Uhr)
        - A8 - canclation day ( wtih help from the system )
                - system help date of canclation * time to end the tour contract vaild ( sameday., 1.2.3week, 1.2.3month,123year)
        - A9 - number of stops per tour 
        - A10- number of paket per tour 
                - if he chose number of paket, will be asked if he want to build up everypaket date - like name addres plaket 
